airtrafficcontrol.app.utils

Class AirCorridorInTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • airtrafficcontrol.app.utils.AirCorridorInTime

  • public class AirCorridorInTime
extends java.lang.Object
    allows to create objects that have a property AltitudeCorridor, where the airplane is supposed to be in the time interval defined by the starting and ending hours.
    Author:
    Eva Gomes, Hugo Leal, Lucas Andrade
